speech: One of the hardest things you will ever have to do my dear, is to grieve the loss of person who is still alive.
Sometimes our fear of loosing someone makes us loose ourself.
You lose yourself trying to hold on to someone who doesn't care losing you.
Don't be afraid of losing someone who doesn't feel lucky to have you.
Don't be the prisoner of your past, be the architect of your future.
Once in a life time  you will meet a person who changes everything in your life
Standing alone is better than standing with people who don't value you.
Warriors are not the one who always win, but the one who always fight.
If people don't hate you then you probably not doing very big things!
Let it hurt , let it bleed , let it heal and let it go.
"I hate two faced people as it makes harder for me to decide on which face i have to slap first."
"Criticize me when you are at my level, until then you may just admire."
Be a good person and don't take time to prove it.
Vanish your distractions , feed your focus.
"I don't care about people who judge me. I'm just going to do whatever makes me happy."
Everyone you meet everyday is fighting a battle you know nothing about. Be kind . Always.
Only those who care about you will hear you when you're quiet.
Don't tell people your plans . Show them your results.
People change , things happen , nothing ever stays the same.
"My attitude is based on how you treat me"
"If you have been hurt many times and you still know how to smile , trust me you are "Damn" strong."
